body_en:
Delete documents

You can run the following cleaning commands:

  • ems:content-type:delete page 
  • ems:content-type:delete new 
  • ems:content-type:delete publication 
  • ems:content-type:delete faq 
  • ems:content-type:delete link 
  • ems:content-type:delete menu 
  • ems:content-type:delete target
  • ems:content-type:delete taxonomy
label: How-to clean a demo website
meta_en: Clean the database in order to initiate a new website
summary_en: In order to develop a new web site you should first clean clean the default structure and adjust some configurations.
